                            <comment id="13642422" author="hustlmsp" created="Fri, 26 Apr 2013 01:20:53 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;the issue would also affect cross region delivery. we need to track the filtered msg id range and last consumed seq id to address the sequence id gap introduced by filter out messages.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13645252" author="hustlmsp" created="Tue, 30 Apr 2013 06:03:30 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;please ignore my previous comment. this fix would be pretty straightforward, just one line: modify the consume seq id in ActiveSubscriberState when #sendingFinished for a filtered out message.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
